This page provides a list of the FHIR artifacts defined as part of this implementation guide.


Structures: Resource Profiles {% capture grouping_desc %}These define constraints on FHIR resources for systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               RareLink Condition for Undiagnosed RD Case

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific Condition profile for documenting undiagnosed rare disease cases based on the IPS Condition profile.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Consent

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific Consent profile based on the Consent resource.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Diagnostic Implication Observation

            {% capture desc %}
  A RareLink-specific profile extending the HL7 Genomics Reporting 'diagnostic-implication' profile 
  for documenting diagnostic significance, evidence levels, and associated phenotypes 
  (genetic_findings.diagnostic_implication).{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Encounter

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific Encounter profile based on the Encounter resource.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Family History

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific FamilyMemberHistory profile based on the FamilyMemberHistory resource.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Genetic Variant Observation

            {% capture desc %}
  A RareLink-specific profile for documenting genetic findings 
  (genetic_findings.variant), based on the HL7 Genomics Reporting variant profile.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink IPS Condition

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific Condition profile based on the IPS Condition profile.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink IPS Measurement Laboratory

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for laboratory measurements based on the IPS Observation profile.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink IPS Measurement Radiology

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for radiology measurements based on the IPS Observation profile.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink IPS Patient

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for the IPS Patient resource.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink IPS Procedure

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for the IPS Procedure resource.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Observation Age Category

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for capturing the age category of
 a patient as an observation, based on the ERDRI-CDS value set.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Observation Gestation at Birth

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for capturing gestation length at birth.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Observation Karyotypic Sex

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for capturing karyotypic sex information.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Observation Measurements (Others)

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for measurements that do not fall under IPS laboratory, radiology, procedures, or vital signs.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Observation Phenotypic Feature

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for capturing phenotypic features.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               RareLink Vital Signs Measurements

            {% capture desc %}A RareLink-specific profile for vital signs measurements.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





Structures: Extension Definitions {% capture grouping_desc %}These define constraints on FHIR data types for systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Age at Diagnosis

            {% capture desc %}ERDRI-CDS - The age at which the condition was diagnosed.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Age at Onset

            {% capture desc %}ERDRI-CDS - The age at which the condition first appeared.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Agreement to Be Contacted

            {% capture desc %}ERDRI-CDS - Agreement to be contacted for research purposes.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Birth Place

            {% capture desc %}The patient's place of birth.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Cause of Death

            {% capture desc %}The cause of death for the patient.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Cause of Death Code

            {% capture desc %}The ICD-10 code representing the cause of death.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Cause of Death Definition

            {% capture desc %}The SNOMED CT definition of the cause of death concept.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Consanguinity

            {% capture desc %}Indicates whether there is consanguinity in the family relationship.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Consent to Reuse Data

            {% capture desc %}ERDRI-CDS - Consent to the reuse of data.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Date of Admission

            {% capture desc %}The date of the patient's admission.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Phenotype Modifier

            {% capture desc %}Captures modifiers for the phenotypic feature, such as severity or specific classifications.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Phenotype Status

            {% capture desc %}Captures the status of a phenotypic feature, such as confirmed present or refuted.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Propositus

            {% capture desc %}Indicates whether the family member is the propositus.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Recorded Sex at Birth

            {% capture desc %}The sex assigned to the patient at birth.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Resolution Date

            {% capture desc %}The date when the phenotypic feature resolved.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Vital Status

            {% capture desc %}Coded representation of a patient's vital status{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





